es</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">Overall Length: 5.5 Inch, Blade Length: 3.25 Inch, Handle Length: 2.25 Inch</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">Includes Reinforced Nylon Sheath</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">Blade: 440 Stainless Steel</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">Color: Chrome</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>6pc Jack Ripper Throwing Knives Set Chrome 440 Stainless Steel - 5.5\"</h1>\n\t\t\t<p>Practice and perfect your your ninja skills with the 6 piece Jack Ripper Throwing Knife Set!\n\nCarefully balanced with the center of gravity in the middle of the knives, these blades will make even, round circles in flight. The single-edged 5.5 inch blades will give you the option to grip them from either the handle or the blade side, and allow for more variation in throwing techniques. \n\nThe 440 stainless steel construction will keep these knives in great condition through many practice sessions. The solid piece of steel from tip to handle ensures you wont have to worry about losing rivets or parts of the handle if you accidentally hit a rock.\n\nIncluded is a reinforced nylon sheath that will hold all six knives. The sheath has a forearm loop that can also be used for a belt attachment for ease of access when using.</p>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
